    "body" : "<p>As you can see <a href=\"http://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/current/javadoc-api/org/springframework/web/bind/annotation/GetMapping.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">here</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Specifically, <code>@GetMapping</code> is a composed annotation that acts as a\n  shortcut for <code>@RequestMapping(method = RequestMethod.GET)</code>.</p>\n  \n  <p>Difference between <code>@GetMapping</code> &amp; <code>@RequestMapping</code></p>\n  \n  <p><code>@GetMapping</code> supports the <code>consumes</code> attribute like\n  <code>@RequestMapping</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
