  "title" : "Difference between the annotations @GetMapping and @RequestMapping(method = RequestMethod.GET)",
  "body" : "<p>What's the difference between <code>@GetMapping</code> and <code>@RequestMapping(method = RequestMethod.GET)</code>?<br />\nI've seen in some Spring Reactive examples, that\n<code>@GetMapping</code> was used instead of <code>@RequestMapping</code>.</p>\n"
